                    "body": "1. You need to install not only {{libarrow-python-dev}} but also {{pkg-config}} because our CMake support has a problem. See  ARROW-12175 for details.\r\n\r\n2. You need to use low-level {{find_library}} and {{find_path}} instead of high-level {{find_package}}.",
